同济医院重症医生陆俊：同事听说我“去世”，大哭了一场。
Tongji Hospital seriously ill doctor Lu Jun: Colleagues heard that I "passed away" and cried a lot.
王瑞文 王亚会。
Wang Ruiwen will be.
